// STRESS 1: type system + multi-word returns + paren-form params + zero-arg call
// edges: int param, double return, list-of-strings return, call helper()
Create a console application.

Make a function called add(int a, int b) that returns an int.
Make a function called pi() that returns a double.
Make a function called tags() that returns a list of strings.
Make a function called helper():
    print helper

When the program starts:
    call add(2, 3)
    call helper
    print done
